        "instruction": "Put the stages of sedimentary rock formation in the correct order.",
        "items": [
          "Older rocks are weathered and eroded into small pieces.",
          "The sediment is transported by rivers, wind, sea, or ice.",
          "The sediment is deposited in layers.",
          "More layers build up and compress the lower sediment.",
          "Dissolved minerals harden and cement the grains together.",
          "The sediment becomes sedimentary rock."
