        "title": "How Igneous Rock Forms",
        "instruction": "Put the stages of igneous rock formation in the correct order.",
        "items": [
          "Rock melts deep inside the Earth to form magma.",
          "The magma rises because it is very hot.",
          "Some magma cools underground, while some erupts as lava.",
          "The molten rock begins to cool.",
          "Mineral crystals grow as cooling continues.",
          "The molten rock solidifies into igneous rock."
        ],
        "shuffle": true
