        "instruction": "Put the stages of metamorphic rock formation in the correct order.",
        "items": [
          "Existing rock is buried deep in the Earth.",
          "Movement in the Earth causes heat and pressure.",
          "The original rock is squashed or heated without melting.",
          "Minerals inside the rock are rearranged.",
          "New crystals can grow within the rock.",
          "The rock becomes metamorphic rock."
